<p class="">That is another assumption on the part of the Prime Minister which is wrong. Will he be good enough to answer my question, and give instructions that as long as there are nationalised assets which are the property of the State he will not permit his Ministers to make speeches which would cause the value of the assets to decline and public money to be wasted?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
